               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17851214-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">21st day of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851214-1-off1 t17851214-1-cd2"></join> last, two woollen cloth coats, value 3 l. one sattin waistcoat, value 10 s. one silk and cotton waistcoat, value 10 s. one woollen cloth waistcoat, value 5 s. two pair of woollen cloth breeches, value 20 s. one pair of shag breeches, value 10 s. one pair of silk breeches, value 10 s. six pair of silk stockings,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178512140003"></xptr> value 20 s. one pair of thread stockings, value 12 d. six linen shirts, value 40 s. three linen handkerchiefs, value 3 s. one pair of leather boots, value 5 s. one man's hat, value 8 s. two leather pocket books, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17851214-1-victim49" type="victimName">Edward Poore<interp inst="t17851214-1-victim49" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851214-1-off1 t17851214-1-victim49"></join>
